OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine, although cloud and patchy
OL,8,Fdrizzle may develop over northern
OL,9,Fhills. Little change overnight, with
OL,10,Fclear spells allowing patchy mist to
OL,11,Fform.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA grey start in places, but
OL,14,Fit will gradually turning brighter and
OL,15,Fsunnier throughout the day. In the
OL,16,Fsunshine and light winds it will feel
OL,17,Fvery warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
